#!/bin/bash

cat <<HereEndsLessonOne

CMake or not CMake, there is no configure.

To build hemp: 

  0) Read the README file         # yeah, right!
  1) Install CMake                # See http://cmake.org/
  2) cd build
  3) cmake ..                     # or "ccmake .." to change defaults
  4) make
  5) make test
  6) sudo make install
  7) Do the happy badger dance!   # optional

See the INSTALL file for further details on building and installing hemp.

HereEndsLessonOne

